{"arkId":"cl010114325","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114325","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Le Sacrifice \u00e0 Lystra, de la tenture des Actes des Ap\u00f4tres","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Le Sacrifice \u00e0 Lystra, de la tenture des Actes des Ap\u00f4tres"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate du mod\u00e8le : vers 1515 - 1516 (mod\u00e8le de la sc\u00e8ne centrale) et vers 1638 (mod\u00e8le de la bordure)\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1638 - 1639 (ancienne datation vers 1630-1635)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1638,"endYear":1639,"imprecision":"vers","text":"2e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1515,"endYear":1516,"imprecision":"vers","text":"1er tiers du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date du mod\u00e8le","doubt":""},{"startYear":1638,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"2e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date du mod\u00e8le","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Santi, Raffaello, dit Rapha\u00ebl","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1520","place":"Rome","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1483","place":"Urbin","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Peintre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q5597"},{"label":"Manufacture de Mortlake","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Atelier de tissage","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Palmer, Sir James","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Sous la direction de","dates":[{"date":"1584","place":"Angleterre","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1657","place":"Angleterre","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"bibliographie\/travail de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q18756800"},{"label":"Clein, Francis","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1582","place":"Rostock, Mecklenbourg-schwerin","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"avant 23\/03\/1658","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Peintre ; Cartonnier","authenticationType":"bibliographie\/travail de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q1906847"},{"label":"Schrijver, Peter","attributionLevel":"Ancienne Attribution","linkType":"?","creatorRole":"Tapissier","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Van der Steen, P.","attributionLevel":"Ancienne Attribution","linkType":"?","creatorRole":"Tapissier","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 5399","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"GMTT 17","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"},{"value":"35","type":"Num\u00e9ro de collection"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"tapisserie ; panneau","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La sc\u00e8ne est tir\u00e9e du passage des Actes des Ap\u00f4tres (chap. 14, versets 8-18)  dans lequel il est dit que Paul - qui est arriv\u00e9 dans la ville de Lystra (ou Lystre) avec Barnab\u00e9 - gu\u00e9rit un paralytique. En voyant cela, la foule les consid\u00e9rant comme deux divinit\u00e9s, pour les remercier, pr\u00e9pare des couronnes et des animaux pour le sacrifice. On voit \u00e0 gauche la population de Lystre, accompagnant les pr\u00eatres de Zeus, au centre, pr\u00eats \u00e0 sacrifier un taureau. Sur la droite, voyant cela, Paul s\u0027appr\u00eate \u00e0 d\u00e9chirer son v\u00eatement et Barnab\u00e9 est en pri\u00e8re. Bordure \u00e0 fond d\u0027or avec des cartouches en cama\u00efeu bronze dor\u00e9 repr\u00e9sentant des sc\u00e8nes du Nouveau Testament, putti, guirlandes de fleurs, fruits dans les angles et au centre de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 ; au centre de la bordure sup\u00e9rieure, un cartouche ovale destin\u00e9 \u00e0 recevoir les armes du propri\u00e9taire ; au centre de la bordure inf\u00e9rieure, un cartouche avec une inscription.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; QVO RAPITIS \/ TAVROS VITTAS \/ CVR NECTITIS VLLAS \/ COR DEVS EXOPTAT \/ NON PETIT ILLE \/ BOVES\r ; Marque de l\u0027atelier : \r ; I.S P [enlac\u00e9s] (marque de Sir James Palmer, gouverneur de la manufacture)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Longueur","value":"538","displayDimension":"538 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"529","displayDimension":"529 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"533","displayDimension":"533 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"726","displayDimension":"726 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"720","displayDimension":"720 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"720","displayDimension":"720 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""},{"type":"Encombrement","value":"538","displayDimension":"538 x 726 cm","unit":"x","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"726 cm","tri":8,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : laine (cha\u00eenes et trames)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : soie (trames)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : m\u00e9tal (fil\u00e9s m\u00e9talliques (\u00e2mes de soie beige recouvertes d\u0027une lame d\u0027argent et\/ou d\u0027argent dor\u00e9))\r\nTechnique : tapisserie = tapisserie sur m\u00e9tier (techniques textile) (r\u00e9duction cha\u00eene : 8 fils\/cm, laine, \u00e9crue ; r\u00e9duction duites : 13-14 duites\/cm, laine, polychrome ; 12-15,5 duites\/cm, soie, polychrome ; 13-17 duites\/cm, fil\u00e9s m\u00e9talliques, argent et or ?)\r\nTechnique : crapautage (techniques textile-\u003Etapisserie = tapisserie sur m\u00e9tier)","placeOfCreation":"Mortlake (Grande-Bretagne = Grande Bretagne-\u003EAngleterre) (dans le Surrey, pr\u00e8s de Londres)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"D\u0027un ensemble de 4 pi\u00e8ces, tiss\u00e9es d\u0027apr\u00e8s les cartons command\u00e9 \u00e0 Rapha\u00ebl par le pape L\u00e9on X pour \u00eatre tiss\u00e9s \u00e0 Bruxelles ; acquis pour le Garde Meuble de la Couronne et inventori\u00e9 au n\u00b035 des tentures \u00e0 or ; Meubles et objets d\u0027art du Garde-Meuble attribu\u00e9s au Louvre par d\u00e9cret du 24 f\u00e9vrier 1901, Archives AN, F21 4438, dans le dossier \u0022Inventaire des tapisseries plac\u00e9es dans les mus\u00e9es nationaux, 1911\u0022 tapisseries 2e liste : dans la liste des tapisseries du Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, cette tapisserie est indiqu\u00e9e comme \u00e9tant dans les salles Mobilier, salle Louis XIV","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mobilier national (ancien Garde Meuble)","note":"","role":", Institution \/ Mus\u00e9e"},{"value":"Louis XIV, roi de France","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"M. Mazarin, Jules","note":" (dans l\u0027inventaire de 1661, al tenture est au  n\u00b0 1704, et est estim\u00e9\u0026e 16 000 livres tournois)","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"versement","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"24\/02\/1901","startYear":1901,"endYear":1901}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Obj